== Commemoration ==
[[File:RSC plaque, Former County Court, Quay Street, Manchester.JPG|thumbnail|right|A [[blue plaque]] erected Quay Street, Manchester]]
The Roscoe Building at the University of Manchester was named after Professor Roscoe: it is a large general-purpose teaching facility used for various levels of teaching in Brunswick Street.<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20040929061919/http://www.man.ac.uk/about/campus.html The University of Manchester: Campus Map]. man.ac.uk.</ref>

